  "title": "Postdoctoral Fellow (Asia Competitiveness Institute) (31527)",
  "description": "<p>Interested applicants are invited to apply directly at the <a href=\"https://careers.nus.edu.sg/job/Postdoctoral-Fellow-%28Asia-Competitiveness-Institute%29-%2831527%29/31527-en_GB/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>NUS\nCareer Portal</strong></a></p><p>Your application will be processed only if you apply\nvia <a href=\"https://careers.nus.edu.sg/job/Postdoctoral-Fellow-%28Asia-Competitiveness-Institute%29-%2831527%29/31527-en_GB/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>NUS\nCareer Portal</strong></a></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br /></p><h2><strong>Job Description</strong></h2><p>The candidate will join our Asia Competitiveness Institute research team to work on a number of projects. </p><p>We are specifically looking for candidates with experience in quantitative research methods and familiar with economic development of Asian countries and economies. Candidate must be comfortable and proficient with statistical software such as STATA, and advanced programming languages.  </p><h2><strong>Qualifications</strong></h2><ul><li>PhD degree in Economics, Mathematics or equivalent</li><li>Familiar with Economic Development of Asian countries and economies, and their trade relationships</li><li>Possess experience in conducting quantitative research will be preferred</li><li>Possess experience in preparing independently literature reviews, data collection and data analysis, etc </li><li>Demonstrate good organisational and analytical skills </li><li>Excellent verbal and written English is required due to the nature of the role</li></ul>",
